    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or aging. Every component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is remarkably clean, reflecting meticulous care and low usage. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in showroom state, offering the closest experience possible to buying it brand new.",
      "price": 49500.0,
